title: Days Of The New-Days Of The New(yellow cover)    FLAC  ak6103
description: Days Of The New-Days Of The New(yellow cover) What we got Travis Meeks Best achievement before His best day was a full bag and a working lighter....this is a classic album that I always have around Its just damn good. The only things I remember about the 2 albums that followed this is one was red and the other green not in that order. Anyway get it if you want it,if you keep it trade me some seeds for it...........
